528
00:28:49,799 --> 00:28:50,839
[chuckling]

529
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:53,840
Jeremy Clarkson,
he can't even drive in a straight line.

530
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:57,880
[Jeremy] There's a bit over there
as well. Jesus wept.

531
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:05,280
