00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:54,400
Yeah, I've farmed this farm
for three years.

548
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,600
-Three years is it?
-Yeah.

549
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:58,480
Well I've been nearly 24 hours

550
00:29:58,559 --> 00:30:02,239
and all I've managed to do is cultivate
ten acres of,

